episodes.title: I am Jesus! - Evil Cults (Documentary)
episodes.description:
Everybody heard some crazy or scary cult stories, but did you know that a lot of followers of these groups believe that their leader is the messiah? A lot of these leaders made their members do some beyond insane things,  and today you will find out more about it! If I missed any cults, let me know in the comments! 

Documentary by The Glymp
